<template #docker>

{# <h2>🐋 Docker Deployment</h2> #}

<h3>Step-by-Step Guide</h3>

<ol>
<li><strong>Download checkpoint:</strong><br>
<a href="{{ links.team_files.url }}">📥 Open in Team Files</a></li>

<li><strong>Pull Docker image:</strong>

   ```bash
   docker pull {{ code.docker.image }}
   ```

</li>

<li><strong>Run container:</strong>

```bash
docker run \
    --runtime=nvidia \
    -v "./{{ artifacts.experiment_dir }}:/model" \
    -p 8000:8000 \
    {{ code.docker.image }} \
    deploy \
    --model "/model/checkpoints/{{ artifacts.best_checkpoint.name }}" \
    --device "cuda:0"
```

</li>

<li><strong>Connect and use:</strong>

```python
from supervisely.nn import ModelAPI

# Connect to local server
model = ModelAPI(url="http://localhost:8000")

# Predict
predictions = model.predict(
    input=["image1.jpg", "image2.jpg"]
)
```

</li>
</ol>

<h3>Quick Prediction</h3>

```bash
docker run \
--runtime=nvidia \
-v "./{{ artifacts.experiment_dir }}:/model" \
{{ code.docker.image }} \
predict \
"./image.jpg" \
--model "/model/checkpoints/{{ artifacts.best_checkpoint.name }}" \
--device "cuda:0"
```

</template>

