## 🎬 Object Tracking in Video

Extend detection capabilities to object tracking in video using **BoxMot**.

### Installation and Usage

```bash
pip install boxmot
```

```python
import supervisely as sly
from supervisely.nn.tracking import track
import boxmot

# Deploy detector
detector = api.nn.deploy(
    model="{{ experiment.framework_name }}/{{ experiment.model_name }}",
    device="cuda:0"
)

# Configure tracker
tracker = boxmot.BotSort(device="cpu")

# Track objects
video_ann = track(
    video_id=42,
    detector=detector,
    tracker=tracker
)
```

> 📚 [Learn more about tracking](https://docs.supervisely.com/neural-networks/overview-1/prediction-api#tracking-objects-in-video)

{% endif %}

